title: Iron Maiden Live After Death - 2 DVds
description:
Iron Maiden Live After Death 

Rock-gods Iron Maiden perform live at Long Beach Arena, California in 1984. 
The 4-night stand saw huge Egyptian sphinxes on either side of the stage and 
a gigantic mummy in the middle shooting pyrotechnic sparks from its eyes; all 
stunningly brought back to life in this DVD.
